        "content": "<p>I have <code>h : ↑m ≤ 1</code>, where <code>m : ℕ</code> and <code>↑m : WithTop ℕ∞</code>. How can I get the inequality <code>m ≤ 1</code>?</p>",
        "id": 565121615,
