    {
        "content": "<p>Is <code>try?</code> the same as <code>apply?</code>?</p>",
        "id": 565124604,
        "sender_full_name": "Michael Novak",
        "timestamp": 1766482332
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>They're complementary. <code>apply?</code> is \"find me a lemma which looks like it fits\". <code>exact?</code> is \"only show me ones which close the goal\". And then <code>try?</code> will look at whether tactics (rather than specific lemmas) will make progress as well, like here.</p>",
        "id": 565125699,
        "sender_full_name": "Julian Berman",
        "timestamp": 1766482858
    }
